Unitron/The Protectobots/Chordate:




Unitron hovered for a few cycles out of firing range of the Element, 
scanning, and picking up Speedbreaker on his radar.  He transformed to biped 
mode and flew off towards him.  "We must speak!"

===

The Protectobots remained in CR chambers.

---

Chordate lay on the ground in the mess hall, passed out and drunk from all 
the alcoholic liquid energon he had ingested.
